   minimizes the discrepancy parallel to theta (m)(x, t) - theta (x, t;
   q(0))parallel to (L2(Gamma 1x{[}0, tmax])) between the temperature
   theta (x, t; q(o)) calculated from the solution of a direct problem for
   each flux q(o) and the desired (or measured) temperature theta (m)(x,
