   flow simulation is here extended to thermo-magnetically driven flows.
   The proposed FEM formulation is used for the calculation of the direct,
   adjoint and sensitivity thermal, fluid flow and electric potential
   fields. The entire optimization algorithm is solved using the conjugate
   gradient method. Finally, the method is demonstrated through the
